WHO   — The Reflexivity Problem — we read the forecast and change
WHAT  — The wall Asimov's own premise concedes: the gas can't read the weather report; people can, and do.
WHERE — POP · Population Dynamics  Framework inputs: ecology, epidemiology, population genetics; Asimov's Foundation; verified & cited  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0 · Life Science)
WHY   — Because the deepest reason human psychohistory stays fiction is also the most hopeful fact about us.
HOW   — By feeding the prediction back into the predicted — who then meet it, beat it, or break it.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Tell the molecules the forecast and nothing changes. Tell the people, and they change everything. That is why I keep psychohistory a dream — and why I am the best news in this whole field.

